volumeInfo.description: Accompanying ... "student CD-ROM contains self-study software that allows you to test your knowledge. It also includes new student-narrated PowerPoint slides that talk you through chapter topics. New Interactive FinSims features hands-on simulations of key concepts to reinforce important topics. You will also find Excel templates that correspond with many end-of-chapter problems, along with additional Web links to the book's Online Learning Center and other important Websites." -- p. [4] of cover.
